    "description": {
      "lore": "Once a decorated member of The Baxter Society, Calico left the august order once she realized that killing monsters for free was less profitable than killing people for money.\n\nNow an in demand contract killer, Calico is living her best life ending someone else's.",
      "playstyle": "Calico uses the shadows to her advantage, weaving in and out of combat to hunt down her enemies one by one.",
      "role": "Wreaks havoc from the sidelines"
    },
