    "description": {
      "lore": "He's proper, he's polite, but the humble Doorman of The Baroness Hotel is more than meets the eye.\n\nWhile he had only planned to experience life on this plane for a few weeks, The Doorman quickly discovered that the New York service industry was a great way to see the strange demands that please humans."
    },
